========================================================
TROUBLESHOOTING
========================================================
1) 404 error
- Project site URL must include repo name:
  https://agroinformatics.github.io/<REPO_NAME>/
- Confirm Pages: main + /docs

2) CSS or fonts not loading
- Confirm `_quarto.yml` includes:
  include-in-header: assets/fonts.html
  theme includes assets/theme.scss
- Re-render + push.

3) Links wrong / navigation broken
- Confirm site-url includes trailing slash and repo name.
- Re-render.

4) `quarto` not found
- Restart VS Code
- Recheck `quarto --version`

5) Pages not updating
- Ensure `docs/` is committed and pushed.
- Check:
  git status
  ls docs
